### Ascend API — Admin Endpoints
### Requires: admin user JWT in @adminToken

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@adminToken = REPLACE_WITH_ADMIN_JWT

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### List all users (paginated)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Search users by name or email
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users?search=john&page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Change a user's role
### Body: { "role": "MODERATOR" } | "USER" | "ADMIN"
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_UUID_HERE/role
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "MODERATOR"
}

###

### Promote user to ADMIN
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_UUID_HERE/role
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Deactivate a user (revokes all sessions)
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_UUID_HERE/active
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": false
}

###

### Re-activate a user
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/users/USER_UUID_HERE/active
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isActive": true
}

###

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Platform statistics
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
